mg src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/baihoc/listening/beginner/bai2/bai2_1.gif" alt="" width="450" height="294" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: x-large;">Listening</span></strong></p>\r\n<p align="center"><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/baihoc/listening/beginner/bai2/bai2_2.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="299" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p>1. First time: Đoạn hội thoại sau l&agrave; cuộc n&oacute;i chuyện giữa hai người bạn mới quen, c&aacute;c bạn h&atilde;y ch&uacute; &yacute; nghe xem hai người đ&oacute; đang n&oacute;i g&igrave; nh&eacute;.</p>\r\n<div id="mediaplayer1_wrapper" style="position: relative; width: 300px; height: 24px;"><object id="mediaplayer1" width="100%" height="100%" name="mediaplayer1" bgcolor="#000000" data="http://www.tienganh123.com/jwplayer/player.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash"><param name="src" value="http://www.tienganh123.com/jwplayer/player.swf" /></object></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="xemdich_1"><input id="xemdich_button_1" type="button" value="Xem b&agrave;i dịch" /></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div id="thongbao_1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong>* Transcript</strong></span>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>Hello.</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>Hello.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>How are you?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>I''m fine, Thank you. And you?</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>I''m fine, thank you. Where are you from?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>I come from England.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>You come from England! Do you like Manchester United?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>Um, I don''t like football.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>Oh, You don''t like football, I see. Why did you come here?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>I came for vacation.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>You came for vacation? Are you having fun?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>Yes, I''m having a great time.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>What do you like best here?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>What do I like best? Well, the people are very kind.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>Yes, the people here are kind. Do you like the food?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>Yes! The food is great!</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>Is the food too spicy for you?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>No, I love spicy food! I can eat spicy food everyday.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;How much longer will you stay here?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:</strong>&nbsp;I will stay two more days.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>Oh! Then you will go home?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>Yes, then I will go home.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>Where do you work?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>I work for a big company.</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>What kind of company do you work for?</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>I work for an import company. And what about you?</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>I work at a bank.</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>Uh. Are you a bank teller?</p>\r\n<p><strong>M:&nbsp;</strong>No, I''m the owner.</p>\r\n<p><strong>W:&nbsp;</strong>Oh.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>2. Second time:&nbsp;<a style="font-size: 10pt; color: #336699; text-decoration: none;" href="/06.WWW/index.php/sysadmin/content/"><span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: large;">Click v&agrave;o đ&acirc;y để nghe v&agrave; l&agrave;m b&agrave;i tập</span></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: x-large;"><strong>Post-listening</strong></span></p>\r\n<strong>1.&nbsp;</strong>Khi n&oacute;i chuyện với một người mới quen, bạn n&ecirc;n n&oacute;i đến những nội dung quen thuộc v&ocirc; thưởng v&ocirc; phạt ( v&iacute; như hỏi qu&ecirc; qu&aacute;n, sở th&iacute;ch, c&ocirc;ng việc)\r\n<p><strong>Eg.</strong>&nbsp;Where are you from?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Do you like Manchester United?</p>\r\n<p><strong>2.&nbsp;</strong>C&oacute; một điều bạn phải đặc biệt lưu &yacute; khi giao tiếp với người lạ, nhất l&agrave; người phương T&acirc;y: kh&ocirc;ng hỏi tuổi, kh&ocirc;ng hỏi tiền lương hoặc những vấn đề ri&ecirc;ng tư kh&aacute;c.</p>\r\n<p>Eg. Tr&aacute;nh hỏi&nbsp;"How old are you?"</p>\r\n<p><strong>3.&nbsp;</strong>Vấn đề g&acirc;y kh&oacute; nghe chuẩn:&nbsp;<em><strong>Ph&aacute;t &acirc;m kh&ocirc;ng chuẩn</strong></em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; t&igrave;nh huống rất phổ biến đối với mọi người khi học tiếng Anh. Nhiều l&uacute;c c&aacute;c bạn kh&ocirc;ng nghe r&otilde; v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng hiểu từ m&igrave;nh nghe được l&agrave; từ g&igrave;,nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n l&agrave; do ph&aacute;t &acirc;m kh&ocirc;ng ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c.</p>\r\n<p>Eg. Một số người vẫn thường ghi như thế n&agrave;y để nhớ c&aacute;ch ph&aacute;t &acirc;m:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/baihoc/listening/beginner/bai2/bai2_3.jpg" alt="" width="277" height="63" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p>nhưng điều n&agrave;y l&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng n&ecirc;n. N&oacute; sẽ l&agrave;m bạn ph&aacute;t &acirc;m sai v&agrave; c&agrave;ng học theo c&aacute;ch đ&oacute;, sau n&agrave;y bạn c&agrave;ng kh&oacute; sửa c&aacute;ch ph&aacute;t &acirc;m của m&igrave;nh cho ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c.</p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c bạn n&ecirc;n học theo bảng sau: (Tham khảo th&ecirc;m trong phần&nbsp;<a style="font-size: 10pt; color: #336699; text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.tienganh123.com/?c=mod-23" target="_blank"><em>b&agrave;i học - ph&aacute;t &acirc;m</em></a><a style="font-size: 10pt; color: #336699;">)</a></p>\r\n<p align="center"><a style="font-size: 10pt; color: #336699;"><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/baihoc/listening/beginner/bai2/phonetics.gif" alt="" width="589" height="377" border="0" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-size: 10pt; color: #336699;">&nbsp;</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: x-large;">B&agrave;i tập: Nghe lại v&agrave; điền từ v&agrave;o &ocirc; trống</span></a></p>\r\n<div id="mediaplayer2_wrapper" style="position: relative; width: 300px; height: 24px;"><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><object id="mediaplayer2" width="100%" height="100%" name="mediaplayer2" bgcolor="#000000" data="http://www.tienganh123.com/jwplayer/player.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash"><param name="src" value="http://www.tienganh123.com/jwplayer/player.swf" /></object></a></div>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;Hello.</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>W:</strong>&nbsp;Hello.</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;<input id="answer0" style="width: 3em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;are you?</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>W:</strong>&nbsp;I''m&nbsp;<input id="answer1" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />, Thank you. And you?</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; color: #336699; line-height: 20px;"><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;I''m fine, thank you. Where are you&nbsp;<input id="answer2" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />?</a></p>\r\n<p><a style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px;