#ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;over the waves. I also really enjoy&nbsp;<input id="answer6" style="width: 7em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> I like dancing to American music because that''s what I know&nbsp;<input id="answer7" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;and I also like salsa and meringue which are more Latin types of music. I also like to&nbsp;<input id="answer8" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;in the woods and to explore. I like to walk through forests and I&rsquo;d like to&nbsp;<input id="answer9" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;rivers.<br /> <br /> I enjoy&nbsp;<input id="answer10" style="width: 7em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;new people too. I like to&nbsp;<input id="answer11" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;out about different ways of&nbsp;<input id="answer12" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />, what different people think, where they''re from and how they&nbsp;<input id="answer13" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />. Probably one of my favorite things is animals. I really&nbsp;<input id="answer14" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;dogs and cats and horses.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> When I was little I always tried to talk my&nbsp;<input id="answer15" style="width: 3em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;in letting me have more animals. But usually she wouldn''t.&nbsp;<br /> So I think now that I&rsquo;m going to have my own&nbsp;<input id="answer16" style="width: 5em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />, I''ll try to get lots of animals.&nbsp;<br /> Some things that I don''t&nbsp;<input id="answer17" style="width: 6em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;like are rude people. Sometimes people are not very nice to&nbsp;<input id="answer18" style="width: 9em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />and that makes me&nbsp;<input id="answer19" style="width: 4em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;bad.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> I also don''t really like&nbsp;<input id="answer20" style="width: 7em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />. I tend to get pretty&nbsp;<input id="answer21" style="width: 5em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;in the car. And it seems like it just takes a long time to get there. One final thing I don''t really like is&nbsp;<input id="answer22" style="width: 7em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />.&nbsp;<br /> Sometimes I&rsquo;m not a very&nbsp;<input id="answer23" style="width: 7em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;person. And I just like to&nbsp;<input id="answer24" style="width: 5em; padding: 3px; border-style: none none dotted; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #666666; color: #ff00ff;" type="text" />&nbsp;things up.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;"><input type="button" value="Check" /></p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: x-large;">Nghe b&agrave;i h&aacute;t</span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;"><strong>Love to Be Loved by You (Marc Terenzi)</strong></p>\r\n<table style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" valign="top" width="400"><object width="400" height="300" data="http://www.youtube.com/v/WsEFMmYmU8o?fs=1&amp;hl=en_US" type="application/x-shockwave-flash"><param name="src" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/WsEFMmYmU8o?fs=1&amp;hl=en_US" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /></object></td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" valign="top" width="300">\r\n<div class="loibh" style="font-size: 12px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid #d9d9d9; height: 288px; line-height: 18px; overflow-y: scroll;">\r\n<p>I can&rsquo;t believe I&rsquo;m standing here<br /> Been waiting for so many years and<br /> Today I found the Queen to reign my heart<br /> You changed my live so patiently<br /> And turned it into something good and real<br /> I feel just like I felt in all my dreams<br /> There are questions hard to answer<br /> Can&rsquo;t you see&hellip;</p>\r\n<p>Chorus:<br /> Baby, tell me how can I tell you<br /> That I love you more than life!<br /> Show me how can I show you<br /> That I&rsquo;m blinded by your light!<br /> When you touch me I can touch you<br /> To find out the dream is true!<br /> I love to be loved by you!</p>\r\n<p>Your looking kind of scared right now<br /> Your waiting for the wedding vows but<br /> I don&rsquo;t know if my tongue&rsquo;s able to talk<br /> Your beauty is just blinding me<br /> Like sunbeams on a summer stream and<br /> I gotta close my eyes to protect me<br /> Can you take my hand and lead me<br /> From here please yeah&hellip;</p>\r\n<p>Chorus:<br /> Baby, tell me how can I tell you<br /> That I love you more than life!<br /> Show me how can I show you<br /> That I&rsquo;m blinded by your light!<br /> When you touch me I can touch you<br /> To find out the dream is true!<br /> I love to be loved, I need to be loved<br /> I love to be loved by you!</p>\r\n<p>I know they gonna say our loves not strong enough to last forever<br /> And I know they gonna say that we&rsquo;ll give up because of any weather<br /> But how can they understand that our love is just heaven sent<br /> We keep on going on and on cause this is where we both belong&hellip;</p>\r\n<p>Chorus:<br /> Baby, tell me how can I tell you<br /> That I love you more than life!<br /> Show me how can I show you<br /> That I&rsquo;m blinded by your light!<br /> When you touch me I can touch you<br /> To find out the dream is true!<br /> I love to be loved, I need to be loved<br /> I love to be loved by you!</p>\r\n<p>Yes I love to be loved by you!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Trong bài học này chúng ta sẽ học cách nói về sở thích và những điều không thích .', 0, NULL, '2012-10-24 08:15:39', 37, 1, NULL, 8, '', '', '');
