(20, 'Episode 1. Pleased to meet you (GREETINGS, INTRODUCTIONS)', 'episode-1-pleased-to-meet-you-greetings-introductions', NULL, '<p>&nbsp;<img style="display: none;" src="http://www.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/bai1/bai1.JPG" alt="" width="199" height="113" /></p>\r\n<table style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center">\r\n<table style="width: 670px;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px;" align="left" valign="top" width="335">\r\n<p><span id="taplayer"><object id="player" width="400" height="300" data="http://www.tienganh123.com/includes/player.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash"><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><param name="flashvars" value="file=http://video2.tienganh123.com/communication_english/episode_01.flv&amp;image=http://video2.tienganh123.com/communication_english/01.png" /><param name="quality" value="high" /><param name="src" value="http://www.tienganh123.com/includes/player.swf" /></object></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt; padding-left: 10px; line-height: 19px;" align="left" valign="top">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class="loibh" style="font-size: 12px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid #d9d9d9; height: 288px; line-height: 18px; overflow-y: scroll;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="translate"><input id="translate_button" type="button" value="Xem b&agrave;i dịch" /></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div id="show_mes">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br /> <strong>Anne, a wine dealer from Singapore, arrives at Adelaide Airport and meets her local buyer, Sarah.</strong>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>Anne walks out with the other passengers...&nbsp;</em><br /> <br /> <strong>ANNE</strong>&nbsp;Excuse me...&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong>SARAH</strong>&nbsp;Anne Lee?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong>ANNE&nbsp;</strong>Yes. Hello&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong>SARAH&nbsp;</strong>I''m Sarah Taylor. I&rsquo;m your new local buyer. Pleased to meet you.&nbsp;<br /> (they shake hands)&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong>ANNE&nbsp;</strong>It''s very kind of you to meet me.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong>SARAH&nbsp;</strong>Oh. Sorry. This is my husband, Mark.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong>MARK</strong>&nbsp;Good morning. How are you?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong>ANNE&nbsp;</strong>Very well thankyou.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong>MARK&nbsp;</strong>How was your flight?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong>ANNE&nbsp;</strong>Actually, I''m a bit tired. It was a very long flight.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong>SARAH&nbsp;</strong>Let''s get your bags.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> The three watch as the bags go around. Anne points.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong>ANNE</strong>&nbsp;That''s mine there! The red one.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong>MARK&nbsp;</strong>It''s heavy!&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong>ANNE</strong>&nbsp;Sorry.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong>SARAH&nbsp;</strong>Don''t worry. Mark''s strong &ndash; aren''t you dear?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong>MARK&nbsp;</strong>No worries.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong>SARAH&nbsp;</strong><br /> Come on. Let''s go to the hotel.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <em>They leave the airport.</em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Tahoma, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px;" align="left">\r\n<table id="table1" style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="4">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" width="18%"><span class="notes_title"><strong>1. CH&Agrave;O HỎI</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;">C&oacute; rất nhiều c&aacute;ch ch&agrave;o hỏi người kh&aacute;c:&nbsp;<br /> Từ th&ocirc;ng thường nhất l&agrave;:&nbsp;<span class="notes_example"><strong>Hello</strong>.</span>&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> Từ n&agrave;y c&oacute; thể sử dụng trong bất k&igrave; t&igrave;nh huống n&agrave;o.&nbsp;<br /> Một từ &iacute;t trang trọng hơn l&agrave;:<strong>&nbsp;<span class="notes_example">Hi!</span></strong>&nbsp;<br /> Chỉ sử dụng<strong>&nbsp;Hi</strong>&nbsp;đối với bạn b&egrave; hoặc trong t&igrave;nh huống &iacute;t trang trọng. &nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="egbg">\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;"><span class="transname">SARAH</span>&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example">Anne Lee?</span><br /> <br /> <span class="transname">ANNE</span><br /> <span class="notes_example">Yes.&nbsp;<strong>Hello<br /> &nbsp;</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" width="82%">Ch&uacute;ng ta cũng d&ugrave;ng:&nbsp;<span class="notes_example"><strong>How are you?</strong></span><strong>&nbsp;</strong><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> hay:&nbsp;<span class="notes_example"><strong>How are you going?</strong></span>&nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;">V&agrave; c&ograve;n c&oacute; thể n&oacute;i:<strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></strong><br /> <span class="notes_example">Good morning</span>&nbsp;(trước 12 giờ trưa)<br /> <span class="notes_example">Good afternoon</span>&nbsp;(12-6 giờ chiều)<br /> <span class="notes_example">Good day</span>&nbsp;(bất cứ l&uacute;c n&agrave;o)<br /> <span class="notes_example">Good evening</span>&nbsp;(sau 6 giờ chiều)<br /> &nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="egbg">\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;"><span class="transname">MARK&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> Good morning. How are you?<br /> &nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div style="padding: 2px 5px; background-color: #d0baad;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<table id="table2" style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="4">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" width="90%"><span class="bold"><strong>C&aacute;ch trả lời</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;">\r\n<p>C&oacute; thể trả lời cho&nbsp;<strong>hello</strong>&nbsp;bằng<strong>&nbsp;hello</strong>.&nbsp;<span class="notes_example"><strong><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> Hello</strong>&nbsp;Peta&nbsp;<br /> <strong>Hello</strong>&nbsp;Trevor</span></p>\r\n<p>Trả lời cho&nbsp;<strong>Hi</strong>&nbsp;bằng&nbsp;<strong>Hi</strong>.&nbsp;<br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>Hi</strong>&nbsp;Peta<br /> <strong>Hi</strong>&nbsp;Trevor</span><br /> <br /> Trả lời cho&nbsp;<strong>Good morning</strong>&nbsp;bằng<strong>&nbsp;Good morning</strong>.<br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>Good morning</strong>&nbsp;Peta.<br /> <strong>Good morning</strong>&nbsp;Trevor.</span>&nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;">Trả lời cho<strong>&nbsp;How are you?</strong>&nbsp;bằng&nbsp;<strong>Good, thanks</strong><span class="notes_example">&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> How are you?<strong>&nbsp;<br /> Good thanks.</strong>&nbsp;</span><br /> <br /> C&acirc;u trả lời kh&aacute;c c&oacute; thể l&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>Fine thanks</strong><br /> <span class="notes_example">How are you?<strong>&nbsp;<br /> Fine thanks.</strong>&nbsp;</span><br /> <br /> hay theo c&aacute;ch suồng s&atilde;&nbsp;<strong>Not bad</strong><br /> <span class="notes_example">How are you?<strong>&nbsp;<br /> Not bad.</strong>&nbsp;</span><br /> <br /> v&agrave; trang trọng hơn với:<strong>&nbsp;Very well thank you.</strong>&nbsp;<br /> <span class="notes_example">How are you?&nbsp;<br /> <strong>Very well thank you.<br /> &nbsp;</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="egbg">\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;"><span class="transname">MARK</span>&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example">Good morning. How are you?</span><br /> <br /> <span class="transname">ANNE</span><span class="notes_example"><strong>&nbsp;<br /> Very well thankyou.</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="padding: 2px 5px; background-color: #d0baad;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<table id="table3" style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="4">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top"><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/logo_box.gif" alt="" width="32" height="19" align="absmiddle" hspace="5" vspace="5" /></td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;"><span class="notes_title"><strong>2.GIỚI THIỆU</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" width="90%">Nếu người bạn gặp kh&ocirc;ng biết t&ecirc;n bạn, bạn h&atilde;y n&oacute;i n&oacute;:&nbsp;<span class="notes_example"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> Hello, I''m</span>......... (t&ecirc;n bạn).&nbsp;<br /> Hay&nbsp;<br /> <span class="notes_example">Good morning. My name is</span>......... (t&ecirc;n bạn).<br /> &nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;">Nếu bạn đang giới thiệu ai đ&oacute;, bạn c&oacute; thể n&oacute;i:<span class="notes_example"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> This is</span>......(t&ecirc;n người đ&oacute;).&nbsp;<br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>This is</strong>&nbsp;Sue Smith.</span>&nbsp;<br /> Hay:&nbsp;<br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>I&rsquo;d like you to meet</strong>&nbsp;Sue Smith.<br /> &nbsp;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;">Th&ocirc;ng thường ch&uacute;ng ta đưa nhiều th&ocirc;ng tin hơn khi giới thiệu ai đ&oacute;:&nbsp;<span class="notes_example"><strong><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> This is my office manager</strong>, Sue Smith.</span>&nbsp;<br /> Hay:&nbsp;<span class="notes_example"><strong>This is my brother</strong>, Phillip Taylor.<br /> &nbsp;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;">C&acirc;u trả lời th&ocirc;ng thường l&agrave;:&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example">Pleased to meet you.</span>&nbsp;<br /> Hay&nbsp;<br /> <span class="notes_example">Nice to meet you.</span>&nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="egbg">\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;"><span class="transname">SARAH&nbsp;</span><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>I&rsquo;m Sarah Taylor. I&rsquo;m your new local buyer. Pleased to meet you.</strong>&nbsp;</span><br /> <span class="uptitledm">(they shake hands)</span>&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">ANNE</span><span class="notes_example">&nbsp;<br /> It&rsquo;s very kind of you to meet me.</span><br /> <br /> <span class="transname">SARAH&nbsp;</span><br /> <span class="notes_example">Oh. Sorry.&nbsp;<strong>This is my husband</strong>, Mark.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="padding: 2px 5px; background-color: #d0baad;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<table id="table4" style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="4">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top"><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/logo_box.gif" alt="" width="32" height="19" align="absmiddle" hspace="5" vspace="5" /></td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;"><span class="notes_title"><strong>3. C&Acirc;U ĐƠN</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" width="90%">\r\n<p>Tiếng Anh được tạo th&agrave;nh từ c&aacute;c c&acirc;u:&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Một c&acirc;u lu&ocirc;n bắt đầu bằng 1 chữ c&aacute;i viết hoa, v&agrave; kết th&uacute;c với dấu chấm c&acirc;u (.), dấu hỏi chấm (?), hay dấu chấm than (!).&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; một c&acirc;u đơn:&nbsp;<br /> <strong>I&rsquo;m Sarah Taylor.</strong>&nbsp;<br /> <br /> C&acirc;u tr&ecirc;n c&oacute; cấu tạo 3 phần:&nbsp;<br /> - Chủ ngữ (The subject<strong>) I.</strong>&nbsp;<br /> - Động từ (The verb)&nbsp;<strong>am.</strong>&nbsp;<br /> - T&acirc;n ngữ (The object)&nbsp;<strong>Sarah Taylor.</strong><br /> <br /> H&atilde;y nh&igrave;n c&acirc;u dưới đ&acirc;y:&nbsp;<br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>She likes wine</strong>.</span><br /> Chủ ngữ l&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>she</strong>.&nbsp;<br /> Động từ l&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>likes</strong>.&nbsp;<br /> T&acirc;n ngữ l&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>wine</strong>.&nbsp;<br /> Chủ ngữ trong c&acirc;u l&agrave; người hay vật thực hiện h&agrave;nh động.&nbsp;<br /> Trong c&acirc;u:<strong>Lions eat meat&nbsp;</strong>th&igrave; chủ ngữ l&agrave;<strong>&nbsp;lions</strong>.&nbsp;<br /> T&acirc;n ngữ của c&acirc;u l&agrave; người hay vật chịu t&aacute;c động của h&agrave;nh động.&nbsp;<br /> Trong c&acirc;u:&nbsp;<strong>Lions eat meat. -&nbsp;</strong>t&acirc;n ngữ l&agrave;<strong>&nbsp;meat</strong>.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="padding: 2px 5px; background-color: #d0baad;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<table id="table5" style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="4">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top"><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/logo_box.gif" alt="" width="32" height="19" align="absmiddle" hspace="5" vspace="5" /></td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;"><span class="notes_title"><strong>4. ĐẠI TỪ CHỈ NGƯỜI</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" width="90%"><strong>Đại từ chỉ người&nbsp;</strong>l&agrave; c&aacute;c từ đại diện cho người.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;"><strong>Đại từ chủ ngữ&nbsp;</strong>l&agrave; chủ ngữ của c&acirc;u.<br /> Ch&uacute;ng gồm:&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>I&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; he&nbsp;&nbsp; she&nbsp;&nbsp; it&nbsp;&nbsp; you&nbsp;&nbsp; we&nbsp;&nbsp; they&nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;"><strong>Đại từ chủ ngữ</strong>&nbsp;thường đứng trước động từ.&nbsp;<br /> V&iacute; dụ:<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>I&nbsp;</strong>like frogs.<br /> &nbsp;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;"><strong>T&iacute;nh từ sở hữu</strong>&nbsp;đi trước danh từ, cho biết ai, hay c&aacute;i g&igrave; sở hữu c&aacute;i g&igrave;.<strong>&nbsp;</strong><br /> V&iacute; dụ:<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example">This is&nbsp;<strong>my</strong>&nbsp;hat.&nbsp;<br /> That is&nbsp;<strong>your</strong>&nbsp;hat.&nbsp;</span><br /> <strong>&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;">C&aacute;c<strong>&nbsp;t&iacute;nh từ sở hữu&nbsp;</strong>bao gồm:&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example">my&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; his&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; her&nbsp;&nbsp; its&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; your&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; our&nbsp;&nbsp; their&nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="egbg" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td class="egbg" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;"><span class="transname">SARAH</span><span class="notes_example">&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> This is&nbsp;<strong>my</strong>&nbsp;husband, Mark.<br /> &nbsp;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;">\r\n<p><strong>Đại từ sở hữu&nbsp;</strong>c&oacute; thể được d&ugrave;ng thay thế cho danh từ:&nbsp;<br /> V&iacute; dụ:<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example">This is my hat.&nbsp;<br /> This is&nbsp;<strong>mine</strong>.&nbsp;<br /> That is your hat.<br /> That is&nbsp;<strong>yours</strong>.</span>&nbsp;<br /> <strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;">C&aacute;c<strong>&nbsp;đại từ sở hữu&nbsp;</strong>gồm c&oacute;: <span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>mine&nbsp;&nbsp; his&nbsp;&nbsp; hers&nbsp;&nbsp; yours&nbsp;&nbsp; ours&nbsp;&nbsp; theirs&nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="egbg" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td class="egbg" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;"><span class="transname">ANNE</span><span class="notes_example">&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> That&rsquo;s<strong>&nbsp;mine</strong>&nbsp;there! The red one.<br /> &nbsp;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="padding: 2px 5px; background-color: #d0baad;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<table id="table6" style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="4">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top"><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/logo_box.gif" alt="" width="32" height="19" align="absmiddle" hspace="5" vspace="5" /></td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;"><span class="notes_title">&nbsp;<strong>5. THIS v&agrave; THAT</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" width="90%"><strong>This</strong>&nbsp;c&oacute; thể được d&ugrave;ng để &aacute;m chỉ c&aacute;c vật hay người ngay cạnh người n&oacute;i.&nbsp;<span class="notes_example"><strong><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> This</strong>&nbsp;is my wife, Mary.&nbsp;<br /> <strong>This</strong>&nbsp;is my watch.<br /> &nbsp;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="egbg" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td class="egbg" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;"><span class="transname">SARAH</span><span class="red"><strong>&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></strong></span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>This</strong>&nbsp;is my husband, Mark.&nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;"><strong>That</strong>&nbsp;được d&ugrave;ng để chỉ c&aacute;c vật hay người ở xa.<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>That</strong>&nbsp;is the man you want to speak to, over there.&nbsp;<br /> <strong>That</strong>&nbsp;is the post office, across the road.&nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="egbg" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td class="egbg" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;"><span class="transname">ANNE</span><span class="red"><strong>&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></strong></span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>That&rsquo;s</strong>&nbsp;mine there! The red one.<br /> &nbsp;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="padding: 2px 5px; background-color: #d0baad;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<table id="table7" style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="4">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top"><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/logo_box.gif" alt="" width="32" height="19" align="absmiddle" hspace="5" vspace="5" /></td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;"><span class="notes_title">&nbsp;<strong>6. T&Iacute;NH TỪ</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" width="90%"><strong>T&iacute;nh từ&nbsp;</strong>mi&ecirc;u tả vật hay người.<br /> C&aacute;c từ như&nbsp;<strong>light, heavy</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>strong</strong>&nbsp;l&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>t&iacute;nh từ</strong><br /> Ch&uacute;ng thường đi trước danh từ, hay sau động từ.<br /> <span class="notes_example">&nbsp;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" align="center" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;">V&iacute; dụ:<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="red">Anne&rsquo;s bag is&nbsp;<strong>heavy</strong>.&nbsp;<br /> It&rsquo;s a&nbsp;<strong>heavy</strong>&nbsp;bag.</span>\r\n<p class="red">The hat is&nbsp;<strong>red</strong>.&nbsp;<br /> It&rsquo;s a&nbsp;<strong>red</strong>&nbsp;hat.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;">B&agrave;i tập thực h&agrave;nh</span></p>\r\n<center style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px;"><br /> </center>', 'Học cách chào hỏi, giới thiệu, thì hiện tại đơn, đại từ chỉ người, This và That, tính từ ', 0, NULL, '2012-10-26 06:25:22', 53, 1, NULL, 18, '', '', ''),
(21, 'Episode 2. Enjoy Your Stay (SAYING THANK YOU, SAYING GOODBYE, PAYING)', 'episode-2-enjoy-your-stay-saying-thank-you-saying-goodbye-paying', NULL, '<p>&nbsp;<img style="display: none;" src="http://www.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/bai2/bai2.JPG" alt="" width="199" height="113" /></p>\r\n<table style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center">\r\n<table style="width: 670px;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px;" align="left" valign="top" width="335">\r\n<p><span id="taplayer"><object id="player" width="400" height="300" data="http://www.tienganh123.com/includes/player.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash"><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><param name="flashvars" value="file=http://video2.tienganh123.com/communication_english/episode_02.flv&amp;image=http://video2.tienganh123.com/communication_english/02.png" /><param name="quality" value="high" /><param name="src" value="http://www.tienganh123.com/includes/player.swf" /></object></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt; padding-left: 10px; line-height: 19px;" align="left" valign="top">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class="loibh" style="font-size: 12px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid #d9d9d9; height: 350px; line-height: 18px; overflow-y: scroll;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="translate"><input id="translate_button" type="button" value="Xem b&agrave;i dịch" /></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div id="show_mes">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br /> <span class="post-title entry-title"><strong>Sarah and Mark take Anne to her hotel. She checks in.</strong></span>&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>ANNE</strong></span>:&nbsp;<span style="cursor: default;">Thank you very much for picking me up.</span>&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>SARAH:&nbsp;</strong></span><span style="cursor: default;">You''re very welcome. Will you be alright here?&nbsp;</span><br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>ANNE</strong></span>:&nbsp;<span style="cursor: default;">Thanks. I''ll be fine. And thankyou Mark, for helping with my heavy bags.</span>&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>MARK</strong></span>:&nbsp;Don''t mention it.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>SARAH</strong></span>:&nbsp;<span style="cursor: default;">Alright then. Nice to meet you finally. I''ll ring you tomorrow.&nbsp;</span><br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>ANNE:&nbsp;</strong></span>Nice to meet you too.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>SARAH:&nbsp;</strong></span>Goodbye.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>CLERK</strong></span>:<span style="cursor: default;">&nbsp;Good morning. Would you like to check in?</span>&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>ANNE</strong></span>:&nbsp;Yes please.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>CLERK</strong></span>:&nbsp;<span style="cursor: default;">And your name?&nbsp;</span><br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>ANNE</strong></span>:&nbsp;Anne Lee.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>CLERK</strong></span>:&nbsp;Ah yes. Could you just fill this out please? How long will you be staying?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>ANNE</strong></span>:&nbsp;Two weeks.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>CLERK</strong></span>:&nbsp;Are you here on business?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>ANNE</strong></span>:&nbsp;<span style="cursor: default;">Mainly business.&nbsp;</span><br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>CLERK</strong></span>:&nbsp;Will you need a hire car?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>ANNE</strong></span>:&nbsp;No thank you.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>CLERK</strong></span>:&nbsp;And will you need a map of the city?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>ANNE</strong></span>:&nbsp;Maybe later.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>CLERK</strong></span>:&nbsp;<span style="cursor: default;">Will you want a newspaper in the morning?&nbsp;</span><br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>ANNE</strong></span>:&nbsp;No thank you.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>CLERK</strong></span>:&nbsp;OK. And how will you be paying Ms Lee?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>ANNE</strong></span>:&nbsp;Credit card.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>CLERK</strong></span>:&nbsp;Thank you. Here''s your key. It''s room 309. Enjoy your stay Ms Lee.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname"><strong>ANNE</strong></span>:&nbsp;Thank you. I hope I will.\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Tahoma, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px;" align="left">\r\n<p><span class="notes_title"><strong>1. N&Oacute;I CẢM ƠN</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;ch phổ biến nhất để cảm ơn người kh&aacute;c l&agrave; n&oacute;i:&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>Thank you</strong></span><br /> C&acirc;u n&agrave;y được n&oacute;i th&agrave;nh 1 từ.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Để nhấn mạnh ta n&oacute;i:&nbsp;<br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>Thank you very much</strong>.</span><br /> Hay:&nbsp;<br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>Thank you so much.</strong></span><br /> <br /> Một từ th&acirc;n mật hơn l&agrave;:<br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>Thanks</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>Một v&agrave;i c&acirc;u trả lời lịch sự cho&nbsp;<strong>thank you</strong>&nbsp;l&agrave;:<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example">Thank you</span><br /> <strong>Don''t mention it.</strong><br /> Hay:<br /> <span class="notes_example">Thanks</span><br /> <strong>You''re welcome.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Một v&agrave;i c&acirc;u trả lời th&acirc;n mật, suồng s&atilde; cho&nbsp;<strong>thank you</strong>&nbsp;hay&nbsp;<strong>thanks</strong>&nbsp;l&agrave;:<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example">Thank you</span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>That''s okay&nbsp;</strong></span><br /> <br /> <span class="notes_example">Thank you very much</span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>That''s fine</strong></span>&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="notes_example">Thanks<br /> <strong>No worries.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">ANNE</span>&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>Thank you very much</strong>&nbsp;for picking me up.</span>&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">SARAH</span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>You''re very welcome</strong>. Will you be alright here?</span>&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">ANNE</span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>Thanks.</strong>&nbsp;I''ll be fine. And&nbsp;<strong>thank you</strong>&nbsp;Mark, for helping with my heavy bags.</span><br /> <br /> <span class="transname">MARK</span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>Don''t mention it.</strong></span><br /> <br /> <img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/logo_box.gif" alt="" width="32" height="19" align="absmiddle" hspace="5" vspace="5" />&nbsp;<span class="notes_title"><strong>2. N&Oacute;I TẠM BIỆT</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>Khi rời ai đ&oacute; ta thường n&oacute;i:<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>Goodbye</strong></span><br /> <br /> Hay th&acirc;n mật hơn:<br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>Bye</strong></span>&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Khi rời 1 người bạn hay ai đ&oacute; bạn c&oacute; thể gặp lại, bạn c&oacute; thể n&oacute;i:<br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>See you later</strong></span><br /> <br /> hay chỉ:<br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>seeya</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">SARAH</span><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <strong>Goodbye.</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/logo_box.gif" alt="" width="32" height="19" align="absmiddle" hspace="5" vspace="5" />&nbsp;<span class="notes_title"><strong>3. TH&Igrave; TƯƠNG LAI</strong></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Th&igrave; tương lai được d&ugrave;ng để n&oacute;i về điều sẽ xảy ra ở tương lai, sau hiện tại.<br /> <br /> Từ&nbsp;<strong>will</strong>&nbsp;được d&ugrave;ng để cho biết ch&uacute;ng ta đang n&oacute;i về tương lai.<br /> <strong>Will</strong>được đặt trước động từ.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Dưới đ&acirc;y l&agrave; 3 c&acirc;u:<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <br /> <strong>Simple Present Tense-Th&igrave; hiện tại đơn giản:</strong>&nbsp;<br /> <span class="notes_example">I go to the city.&nbsp;</span>(t&ocirc;i tới đ&oacute; h&agrave;ng ng&agrave;y)<br /> <br /> <strong>Present Continuous Tense-Th&igrave; hiện tại tiếp diễn:</strong><br /> <span class="notes_example">I am going to the city.</span>&nbsp;(t&ocirc;i đang đi tới đ&oacute;)&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong>Th&igrave; tương lai đơn:</strong><br /> <span class="notes_example">I&nbsp;<strong>will&nbsp;</strong>go to the city.</span>&nbsp;(v&agrave;o thời gian muộn hơn)&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Ch&uacute; &yacute; rằng từ&nbsp;<strong>will</strong>&nbsp;đi trước động từ&nbsp;<strong>go</strong>.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Để biến c&acirc;u tr&ecirc;n th&agrave;nh c&acirc;u hỏi, thay đổi vị tr&iacute; của chủ ngữ&nbsp;<strong>I</strong>&nbsp;v&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>will</strong>.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Will I&nbsp;</strong>go to the city?&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">CLERK</span>&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span>&nbsp;<br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>Will you</strong>&nbsp;need a hire car?</span>&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">CLERK</span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>Will you&nbsp;</strong>want a newspaper in the morning?<strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>Trong văn n&oacute;i, từ&nbsp;<strong>will</strong>&nbsp;thường được n&oacute;i tắt.<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <br /> I will th&agrave;nh&nbsp;<strong>I''ll</strong>.&nbsp;<br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>I''ll</strong>&nbsp;go to the city.</span><br /> <br /> He will th&agrave;nh&nbsp;<strong>he''ll</strong>.&nbsp;<br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>He''ll</strong>&nbsp;get into trouble.</span><br /> <br /> We will th&agrave;nh&nbsp;<strong>we''ll</strong>&nbsp;<br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>We''ll</strong>&nbsp;go out tonight&nbsp;</span><br /> <br /> You will th&agrave;nh&nbsp;<strong>you''ll</strong>.&nbsp;<br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>You''ll</strong>&nbsp;go to the city.</span><br /> <br /> They will th&agrave;nh&nbsp;<strong>they''ll</strong>.<br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>They''ll</strong>&nbsp;lose all their money.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>Nhưng trong c&acirc;u hỏi,&nbsp;<strong>will</strong>&nbsp;được ph&aacute;t &acirc;m đầy đủ.<br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>Will</strong>&nbsp;you go to the city?&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">SARAH</span><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>Will</strong>&nbsp;you be alright here?</span>&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">ANNE</span><br /> <span class="notes_example">Thanks.&nbsp;<strong>I''ll</strong>&nbsp;be fine.</span></p>\r\n<p><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/logo_box.gif" alt="" width="32" height="19" align="absmiddle" hspace="5" vspace="5" />&nbsp;<span class="notes_title"><strong>4. TRẢ TIỀN</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>Khi mua c&aacute;i g&igrave;, người thư k&iacute;, hay trợ l&iacute; b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng c&oacute; thể hỏi:<br /> <span class="notes_example">How will you be paying?</span><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> Hay:<br /> <span class="notes_example">How would you like to pay for that?</span><br /> &nbsp; Bạn c&oacute; thể trả lời:&nbsp;<br /> <img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/02_card.gif" alt="Credit Card" width="60" height="60" align="left" hspace="2" vspace="2" /><span class="notes_example">How will you be paying?</span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>I''d like to pay by</strong>&nbsp;<strong>credit card</strong>.</span>&nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br /> &nbsp;<span class="notes_example"><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/02_cheque.gif" alt="Cheque" width="60" height="60" align="left" hspace="2" vspace="2" /></span>&nbsp;<span class="notes_example">How will you be paying?&nbsp;<br /> <strong>By cheque.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="notes_example"><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/02_cash.gif" alt="Cash" width="60" height="60" align="left" hspace="2" vspace="2" />How will you be paying?<br /> <strong>In cash.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">CLERK</span><br /> <span class="notes_example">And&nbsp;<strong>how will you be paying&nbsp;</strong>Ms Lee?</span>&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">ANNE</span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>Credit card.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/logo_box.gif" alt="" width="32" height="19" align="absmiddle" hspace="5" vspace="5" />&nbsp;<span class="notes_title"><strong>5. TƯỚC VỊ, DANH HIỆU TRANG TRỌNG</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>Khi n&oacute;i chuyện với ai một c&aacute;ch trang trọng, đặc biệt l&agrave; khi gặp họ lần đầu, ta thường d&ugrave;ng&nbsp;<strong>tước vị trang trọng</strong>&nbsp;của họ.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Điều n&agrave;y được thực hiện bằng c&aacute;ch n&oacute;i:<br /> <strong>Mister</strong>&nbsp;(viết&nbsp;<strong>Mr</strong>) cho nam giới.<br /> <strong>Missus</strong>&nbsp;(viết&nbsp;<strong>Mrs</strong>) cho nữ giới.<br /> <strong>Miss</strong>&nbsp;cho phụ nữ chưa kết h&ocirc;n.<br /> Hay&nbsp;<strong>Ms</strong>&nbsp;cho phụ nữ khi bạn kh&ocirc;ng r&otilde; họ đ&atilde; kết h&ocirc;n hay chưa.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Nhiều phụ nữ phương T&acirc;y th&iacute;ch được gọi l&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>Ms</strong>, v&agrave; tốt hơn hết l&agrave; d&ugrave;ng từ n&agrave;y khi kh&ocirc;ng chắc chắn.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Ch&uacute;ng ta n&oacute;i tước vị của 1 người, theo sau bằng họ (<strong>family name</strong>) của người đ&oacute;. Trong tiếng Anh, họ c&ograve;n được gọi l&agrave;<strong>surname</strong>. Đ&ocirc;i khi n&oacute; c&ograve;n được gọi l&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>last name</strong>, v&igrave; được viết cuối c&ugrave;ng.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> V&igrave; vậy, tước vị trang trọng của Brenton Whittle l&agrave;:<br /> <strong>Mr Whittle.</strong>&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Tước vị trang trọng của Michelle Crowden c&oacute; thể l&agrave;:<br /> <strong>Mrs Crowden</strong>&nbsp;(nếu c&ocirc; ấy đ&atilde; kết h&ocirc;n)<br /> <strong>Miss Crowden</strong>&nbsp;(nếu c&ocirc; ấy chưa kết h&ocirc;n)<br /> hay<br /> <strong>Ms Crowden</strong>&nbsp;(trong 1 trong 2 trường hợp tr&ecirc;n).&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Khi bạn đ&atilde; biết ai đ&oacute; r&otilde; hơn, hay trong trường hợp th&acirc;n mật, ta d&ugrave;ng t&ecirc;n ch&iacute;nh (first name) của họ. Tại c&aacute;c nước phương T&acirc;y, đ&acirc;y c&ograve;n được gọi l&agrave;<strong>&nbsp;Christian</strong>&nbsp;name.<br /> <br /> V&igrave; vậy, t&ecirc;n ch&iacute;nh của Brenton Whittle l&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>Brenton</strong>.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Lưu &yacute;: kh&ocirc;ng bao giờ đặt&nbsp;<strong>Mr, Mrs</strong>&nbsp;hay&nbsp;<strong>Ms</strong>&nbsp;trước t&ecirc;n ch&iacute;nh (first name), chỉ trước họ (surname) m&agrave; th&ocirc;i.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Học cách nói cám ơn, nói tạm biệt, thì tương lai, cách trả tiền, tước vị và danh hiệu trang trọng', 0, NULL, '2012-10-26 06:27:37', 6, 1, NULL, 18, '', '', '');
