(22, 'Episode 3. What time is it? (MAKING AN APPOINTMENT, THE TIME) ', 'episode-3-what-time-is-it-making-an-appointment-the-time', NULL, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; line-height: 23px;">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<table style="font-size: 13px; width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;" align="center">\r\n<table style="width: 670px;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px;" align="left" valign="top" width="335">\r\n<p><span id="taplayer"><object id="player" width="400" height="300" data="http://www.tienganh123.com/includes/player.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash"><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><param name="flashvars" value="file=http://video2.tienganh123.com/communication_english/episode_03.flv&amp;image=http://video2.tienganh123.com/communication_english/03.png" /><param name="quality" value="high" /><param name="src" value="http://www.tienganh123.com/includes/player.swf" /></object></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt; padding-left: 10px; line-height: 19px;" align="left" valign="top">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class="loibh" style="font-size: 12px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid #d9d9d9; height: 288px; line-height: 18px; overflow-y: scroll;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="translate"><input id="translate_button" type="button" value="Xem b&agrave;i dịch" /></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div id="show_mes">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="post-title entry-title"><strong>In her hotel room, Anne rings a number. John Barbour, the private detective, answers the phone.</strong>&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">JOHN</span>:&nbsp;Hello, Barbour''s Private Investigation. John Barbour speaking.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">ANNE</span>:&nbsp;Hello. Can you find missing people?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">JOHN</span>:&nbsp;Sometimes we can. Have you lost somebody?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">ANN</span>:&nbsp;Yes.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">JOHN</span>:&nbsp;Perhaps you''d like to tell me about it?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">ANN</span>:&nbsp;Can I make an appointment please?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">JOHN</span>:&nbsp;When would you like to come in?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">ANN</span>E:&nbsp;Is tomorrow okay?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">JOHN</span>:&nbsp;Let''s see&hellip; Yes, I can see you at ten o''clock. Will that suit you?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">ANNE</span>:&nbsp;Okay, thank you.&nbsp;<em>(consults business card)</em>&nbsp;23 Mitchell Street &ndash; is that right?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">JOHN</span>:&nbsp;That''s right. Second floor.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">ANNE</span>:&nbsp;Okay. See you then. Goodbye.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">JOHN</span>:&nbsp;Goodbye.</p>\r\n<p class="post-title entry-title"><em>He puts down the phone and celebrates.<br /> <br /> In her hotel room, Anne puts the phone down, and rings again.</em>&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">CLERK</span>:&nbsp;Hello?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">ANNE</span>:&nbsp;Hello. Reception? What time is it please?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">CLERK</span>:&nbsp;It''s five o''clock.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">ANNE</span>:&nbsp;And what time do you serve dinner?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">CLERK</span>:&nbsp;The restaurant opens in an hour, and dinner is served between six and nine pm.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">ANNE</span>:&nbsp;And breakfast?&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">CLERK</span>:&nbsp;Breakfast is served between seven and nine thirty am ma''am.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">ANNE</span>:&nbsp;Thank you.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <span class="transname">CLERK</span>:&nbsp;You''re welcome.</p>\r\n<p class="post-title entry-title"><em>Anne puts the phone down, then notices the photo by her bed and picks it up again. There is a tear in her eye.</em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Tahoma, Verdana, Arial; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 19px;" align="left">\r\n<p><span class="notes_title"><strong>1. ĐẶT HẸN</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">ANNE</span><span class="notes_example">: Can I make an appointment please?<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></span><br /> <br /> <span class="transname">JOHN</span>:&nbsp;<span class="notes_example">When would you like to come in?</span></p>\r\n<p>Khi n&oacute;i đến một thời điểm x&aacute;c định, ta d&ugrave;ng&nbsp;<strong>at</strong>.<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><em>I''ll see you<strong>&nbsp;at</strong>&nbsp;ten o''clock.<br /> I''ll see you&nbsp;<strong>at&nbsp;</strong>half-past four.</em></span></p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">JOHN</span>:&nbsp;<span class="notes_example">Let''s see&hellip; Yes, I can see you&nbsp;<strong>at&nbsp;</strong>ten o''clock.</span>&nbsp;<span class="notes_example"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></p>\r\n<div align="center">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br /> <img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/logo_box.gif" alt="" width="32" height="19" align="absmiddle" hspace="5" vspace="5" />&nbsp;<span class="notes_title"><strong>2. CAN</strong></span>\r\n<p><strong>Can</strong>&nbsp;nghĩa l&agrave; ''c&oacute; năng lực l&agrave;m g&igrave;''.&nbsp;<br /> I can see you = I am able to see you.</p>\r\n<p>Để đặt c&acirc;u hỏi với&nbsp;<strong>can</strong>, h&atilde;y thay đổi vị tr&iacute; của&nbsp;<strong>I</strong>&nbsp;v&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>can</strong>&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></p>\r\n<table id="table1" style="width: 60%;" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="4">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" width="50%"><strong>Statement</strong><br /> <span class="notes_example">I can see you.&nbsp;<br /> He can see you.&nbsp;<br /> We can see you.&nbsp;<br /> They can see you.&nbsp;</span><br /> <br /> &nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" width="50%"><em><strong>Question&nbsp;</strong></em><br /> <span class="notes_example"><em>Can I see you?&nbsp;<br /> Can he see you?&nbsp;<br /> Can we see you?</em>&nbsp;<br /> <em>Can they see you?&nbsp;</em></span><br /> <em>&nbsp;</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br /> <span class="transname">ANNE</span><span class="notes_example"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <strong>Can you</strong>&nbsp;find missing people?</span><br /> <br /> <span class="transname">JOHN</span><br /> <span class="notes_example">Sometimes&nbsp;<strong>we can</strong>.</span>\r\n<p><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/logo_box.gif" alt="" width="32" height="19" align="absmiddle" hspace="5" vspace="5" />&nbsp;<span class="notes_title"><strong>3. WILLv&agrave; ''LL</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>Như ch&uacute;ng ta đ&atilde; gặp, từ&nbsp;<strong>will</strong>&nbsp;được sử dụng để cho biết ch&uacute;ng ta đang n&oacute;i về tương lai.<br /> <em>I&nbsp;<strong>will</strong>&nbsp;see you tomorrow.</em><br /> <br /> Th&ocirc;ng thường, trong hội thoại, ch&uacute;ng ta r&uacute;t ngắn th&agrave;nh:<br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong><em>I''ll&nbsp;</em></strong><em>see you tomorrow.</em></span></p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c từ được viết tắt kh&aacute;c gồm:<span class="notes_example"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <strong>he will&nbsp;<span class="notes_example"><em>he''ll</em></span></strong><br /> <strong>she will</strong>&nbsp;<span class="notes_example"><em><strong>she''ll</strong></em></span><br /> <strong>it will&nbsp;<span class="notes_example"><em>it''ll</em></span></strong><br /> <strong>you will&nbsp;<span class="notes_example"><em>you''ll</em></span></strong><br /> <strong>we will&nbsp;<span class="notes_example"><em>we''ll</em></span></strong><br /> <strong>they will&nbsp;<span class="notes_example"><em>they''ll &nbsp;</em></span></strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/logo_box.gif" alt="" width="32" height="19" align="absmiddle" hspace="5" vspace="5" />&nbsp;<span class="notes_title"><strong>4. THỜI GIAN</strong></span>\r\n<p>Đối với giờ ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c ta d&ugrave;ng&nbsp;<strong>o'' clock</strong>.<br /> <span class="notes_example">4:00 = It''s four o''clock.</span><br /> <span class="notes_example">10:00 = It''s ten o''clock.&nbsp;</span><br /> Ch&uacute;ng ta cũng c&oacute; thể chỉ n&oacute;i:<span class="notes_example"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><em>It''s ten.</em></span><br /> <br /> Th&ocirc;ng thường d&ugrave;ng&nbsp;<strong>a.m</strong>.(cho bất cứ thời gian n&agrave;o sau 12 giờ đ&ecirc;m tới 12 giờ trưa.)&nbsp;<br /> hay&nbsp;<strong>p.m</strong>. (cho bất cứ thời gian n&agrave;o sau 12 giờ trưa tới 12 giờ đ&ecirc;m.).&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p><em><strong>It''s ten a.m.</strong></em><span class="notes_example"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> hay<br /> <em><strong>It''s ten p.m.</strong></em></p>\r\n<p>Đối với giờ rưỡi, ta d&ugrave;ng&nbsp;<strong>half-past</strong>.<span class="notes_example"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <strong>4:30 = It''s half-past four.</strong><br /> hay chỉ cần n&oacute;i:<br /> <span class="notes_example"><em><strong>It''s four-thirty</strong></em></span><strong>&nbsp;(p.m. or a.m.).</strong></p>\r\n<p>Đối với 1/4 giờ ta n&oacute;i:&nbsp;<strong>a quarter past</strong>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<strong>a quarter to</strong>.<span class="notes_example"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example"><strong>4:15 = It''s a quarter past four.<br /> 4:45 = It''s a quarter to five.</strong></span><br /> Hay chỉ cần n&oacute;i:<br /> <strong><em>It''s four fifteen.</em></strong><br /> <span class="notes_example"><em><strong>It''s four forty-five.</strong></em></span><br /> <br /> Đối với bất cứ thời gian n&agrave;o ta đều c&oacute; thể n&oacute;i 1 lượng ph&uacute;t dưới nửa giờ&nbsp;<strong>past&nbsp;</strong>một giờ, hay một lượng ph&uacute;t dưới nửa giờ&nbsp;<strong>to</strong>một giờ n&agrave;o đ&oacute;.</p>\r\n<p><strong>4:10 = It''s ten past four<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> 4:25 = It''s twenty-five past four.<br /> 4:35 = It''s twenty-five to five.<br /> 4:50 = It''s ten to five.</strong><br /> Hay chỉ cần n&oacute;i:<br /> <em><strong>It''s four ten; four twenty-five; four thirty-five; or four fifty.&nbsp;</strong></em>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/logo_box.gif" alt="" width="32" height="19" align="absmiddle" hspace="5" vspace="5" />&nbsp;<span class="notes_title"><strong>5. GIỚI TỪ CHỈ THỜI GIAN</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>C&aacute;c giới từ chỉ thời gian gồm:<br /> <strong>in</strong>;&nbsp;<strong>at</strong>;&nbsp;<strong>on</strong>;&nbsp;<strong>for</strong>;&nbsp;<strong>from</strong>;&nbsp;<strong>until</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>at</strong>&nbsp;= 1 thời điểm x&aacute;c định.<br /> <span class="notes_example"><em>I''ll see you&nbsp;<strong>at</strong>&nbsp;ten o''clock.&nbsp;</em></span><span class="notes_example"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">JOHN</span><span class="notes_example">&nbsp;<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></span><br /> <span class="notes_example">Let''s see&hellip; Yes, I can see you&nbsp;<strong>at</strong>&nbsp;ten o''clock.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>in</strong>= 1 lượng thời gian trong tương lai.<br /> <em>I''ll see you&nbsp;<strong>in</strong>&nbsp;an hour.<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> I''ll see you&nbsp;<strong>in</strong>&nbsp;a week.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">CLERK&nbsp;</span><span class="notes_example"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example">The restaurant opens<strong>&nbsp;in</strong>&nbsp;an hour, and dinner is served between six and nine pm.</span>&nbsp;<span class="notes_example">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>on<em>&nbsp;</em></strong>= 1 thứ trong tuần hay 1 ng&agrave;y trong năm<br /> <em>I''ll see you&nbsp;<strong>on</strong>&nbsp;Wednesday.<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> I saw you&nbsp;<strong>on</strong>&nbsp;the 30th of June.</em></p>\r\n<p><strong>for<em>&nbsp;</em></strong>= 1 lượng thời gian 1 hoạt động diễn ra.<br /> <span class="notes_example"><em>I''ll see you&nbsp;<strong>for</strong>&nbsp;an hour.<span style="cursor: pointer;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> I''ve been sick&nbsp;<strong>for</strong>&nbsp;a week.</em></span></p>\r\n<p><strong>from</strong>&nbsp;= thời điểm h&agrave;nh động bắt đầu.&nbsp;<br /> <strong>until<em>&nbsp;</em></strong>= thời điểm h&agrave;nh động kết th&uacute;c.<br /> <em>They worked&nbsp;<strong>from</strong>&nbsp;9a.m.&nbsp;<strong>until</strong>&nbsp;5 p.m.</em>&nbsp;<span class="notes_example"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></p>\r\n<p>Ch&uacute;ng ta cũng d&ugrave;ng&nbsp;<strong>between</strong>&nbsp;để mi&ecirc;u tả thời gian.<br /> <span class="notes_example"><em>They were working&nbsp;<strong>between</strong>&nbsp;9 a.m. and 5 p.m.</em></span>&nbsp;<span class="notes_example"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">CLERK</span><span class="notes_example"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /> <span class="notes_example">The restaurant opens in an hour, and dinner is served&nbsp;<strong>between&nbsp;</strong>six and nine pm.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 13px;">B&agrave;i tập thực h&agrave;nh</span></p>\r\n<center style="font-size: 13px;"><br /> </center>', '', 0, NULL, '2012-10-26 06:29:18', 10, 0, NULL, 18, '<p>oOo</p>', '<p>opp</p>', ''),
(23, 'Episode 4. Second on the Left (ASKING DIRECTIONS, VISITING)', 'episode-4-second-on-the-left-asking-directions-visiting', NULL, '<p><span class="notes_title"><strong><img style="display: none;" src="http://www.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/bai4/bai4.JPG" alt="" width="200" height="113" /></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span class="notes_title"><strong>1. HỎI ĐƯỜNG</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>Đầu ti&ecirc;n, để thu h&uacute;t sự ch&uacute; &yacute; của người kh&aacute;c:<br /><span class="notes_example">Excuse me.</span><span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span>Để hỏi đường:</span><br /><span class="notes_example">Could you tell me how to get to.... ?</span><br /><span>Hay:</span><br /><span class="notes_example">I''m looking for.... Can you help me?</span><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">ANNE</span><span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /><span class="notes_example"><strong>Excuse me</strong>.</span></p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">WOMAN</span><br /><span class="notes_example">Yes?</span></p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">ANNE</span><br /><span class="notes_example"><strong>Could you tell me how to get to</strong>&nbsp;Mitchell Street?&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">ANNE</span><span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /><span class="notes_example"><strong>Excuse me.<br /><br /></strong></span><span class="transname">SHOPKEEPER</span><br /><span class="notes_example">Yes?</span><span class="transname"><br /><br />ANNE</span><br /><span class="notes_example"><strong>I''m looking for</strong>&nbsp;number 23.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>Kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute;&nbsp;<em><strong>the</strong></em>&nbsp;ở trước t&ecirc;n phố v&agrave;&nbsp; địa chỉ .<br /><span class="notes_example">Could you tell me how to get to Smith Street?&nbsp;<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br />I''m looking for 23 Mitchell Street. Can you help me?&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div>Một v&agrave;i từ c&oacute; thể c&oacute;&nbsp;<strong>the</strong>&nbsp;đứng trước.&nbsp;<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /><span class="notes_example">Could you tell me how to get to&nbsp;<strong>the</strong>&nbsp;police station?<br />I''m looking for&nbsp;<strong>the</strong>&nbsp;airport. Can you help me?</span>&nbsp;<br /><br />&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><span class="transname">WOMAN</span><br /><span class="notes_example">You need to go straight along here, past&nbsp;<strong>the</strong>&nbsp;silver balls, turn left, and it''s the second on the right, opposite&nbsp;<strong>the</strong>&nbsp;Town Hall.</span><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/logo_box.gif" alt="" width="32" height="19" align="absmiddle" hspace="5" vspace="5" />&nbsp;<span class="notes_title"><strong>2. PRESENT CONTINUOUS TENSE</strong></span>&nbsp;<strong>(TH&Igrave; HIỆN TẠI TIẾP DIỄN)</strong></p>\r\n<p>Th&igrave; hiện tại tiếp diễn mi&ecirc;u tả h&agrave;nh động xảy ra ở hiện tại, v&agrave;&nbsp; tiếp tục đến tương lai.</p>\r\n<p>D&ugrave;ng ''to be'' (<strong><em>am, is, are</em></strong>) v&agrave;&nbsp; th&ecirc;m<strong>&nbsp;<em>''ing''</em></strong>&nbsp;ở cuối động từ chỉ h&agrave;nh động.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p><span class="notes_example">I&nbsp;<strong>am</strong>&nbsp;runn<strong>ing</strong>.<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br />He, she or it&nbsp;<em><strong>is</strong></em>&nbsp;runn<strong>ing</strong>.<br />You&nbsp;<strong>are</strong>&nbsp;runn<em><strong>ing</strong></em>.<br />We&nbsp;<em><strong>are</strong></em>&nbsp;runn<em><strong>ing</strong></em>.<br />They&nbsp;<em><strong>are</strong></em>&nbsp;runn<em><strong>ing</strong></em>.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span>Ch&uacute;ng ta thường n&oacute;i tắt trong văn n&oacute;i.</span><span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /><span class="notes_example"><strong>I''m</strong>&nbsp;running.<br /><strong>He''s</strong>&nbsp;running.<br /><strong>You''re</strong>&nbsp;running.<br /><strong>We''re</strong>&nbsp;running.<br /><strong>They''re</strong>&nbsp;running.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">WOMAN</span><span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /><span class="notes_example">Yes. You''<strong>re</strong>&nbsp;go<strong>ing</strong>&nbsp;the wrong way.</span></p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">ANNE</span><br /><span class="notes_example">I''<strong>m</strong>&nbsp;look<strong>ing</strong>&nbsp;for number 23</span></p>\r\n<p><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/logo_box.gif" alt="" width="32" height="19" align="absmiddle" hspace="5" vspace="5" /><span>&nbsp;</span><span class="notes_title"><strong>3. ĐẾN THĂM AI Đ&Oacute;</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>Khi c&oacute; người g&otilde; cửa:&nbsp;<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /><span class="notes_example">Come in!</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>ANNE enters the building and goes up the stairs. She knocks at the door.</em></p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">JOHN</span><span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /><strong>Come in!&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Ch&agrave;o người m&igrave;nh đang đợi:<br /><span class="notes_example">You must be....</span><strong><span class="notes_example"><em>&nbsp;</em></span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">JOHN</span>&nbsp;<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /><span class="notes_example"><strong>You must be</strong>&nbsp;Ms Lee.</span></p>\r\n<p>Bảo ai ngồi xuống:&nbsp;<br /><span class="notes_example"><strong>Please sit down.</strong><br /><strong>Won''t you sit down?</strong>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">JOHN&nbsp;</span><span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /><span class="notes_example">You must be Ms Lee.&nbsp;<strong>Please sit down.</strong></span><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p><span>&Acirc;&nbsp; Đề nghị l&agrave;m việc g&igrave; gi&uacute;p ai (một c&aacute;ch chuy&ecirc;n nghiệp).</span><br /><span class="notes_example">What can I do for you?</span></p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">JOHN&nbsp;</span><span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br /><span class="notes_example">Now -&nbsp;<strong>what can I do for you</strong>&nbsp;Ms Lee?</span><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p><span>&Acirc;&nbsp;&Acirc;&nbsp;&Acirc;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/logo_box.gif" alt="" width="32" height="19" align="absmiddle" hspace="5" vspace="5" /><span>&nbsp;</span><span class="notes_title"><strong>4. CHỈ DẪN</strong></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>H&atilde;y nh&igrave;n bản đồ dưới đ&acirc;y:</span><strong><br /><br /><img src="http://noidung.tienganh123.com/file/giaotrinh/communication/ep_4map.jpg" alt="" width="320" height="224" />&nbsp;<br /></strong><strong>T&igrave;m Victoria Square.<br /></strong><em>If you want to go to Parliament House,&nbsp;<strong>go straight ahead</strong>. (or&nbsp;<strong>straight along</strong>)<br />If you want to go to Flinders Street, turn&nbsp;<strong>to the right</strong>.<br />Waymouth Street is the&nbsp;<strong>second on the left</strong>.</em><span>&nbsp;</span><strong>Find Parliament House.<br /></strong><em>Parliament House is&nbsp;<strong>opposite</strong>&nbsp;Government House.<br />Adelaide Casino is&nbsp;<strong>next to</strong>&nbsp;Parliament House.<br />Adelaide Casino is&nbsp;<strong>between</strong>&nbsp;Parliament House and Adelaide Station.<br />Adelaide Casino is<strong>&nbsp;to the left&nbsp;</strong>of Parliament House.<br />Adeliaide Casino is&nbsp;<strong>to the right</strong>&nbsp;of Adelaide Station.</em></p>\r\n<p><span class="transname">WOMAN</span>&nbsp;<span class="notes_example"><br />You need to go&nbsp;<strong>straight along</strong>&nbsp;here, past the silver balls,&nbsp;<strong>turn left,</strong>&nbsp;and it''s the&nbsp;<strong>second on the right, opposite</strong>&nbsp;the Town Hall.</span></p>', 'Học cách hỏi đường - Thời hiện tại tiếp diễn - thăm quan - phương hướng', 0, NULL, '2012-10-26 06:30:22', 41, 1, NULL, 18, '<p><object width="400" height="300" data="/06.WWW/assets/40251131/plugins/media/moxieplayer.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash"><param name="src" value="/06.WWW/assets/40251131/plugins/media/moxieplayer.swf" /><param name="flashvars" value="url=/06.WWW/uploads/Video/tham_khao/ep4/Episode%25204.%2520Second%2520on%2520the%2520Left%2520%2528ASKING%2520DIRECTIONS%252C%2520VISITING%2529%2520_raquo%253B%2520Communication%2520English%2520_raquo%253B%2520Tham%2520kh%25E1%25BA%25A3o.flv&amp;poster=/06.WWW/index.php/sysadmin/content/" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="true" /></object></p>', '<p><a title="Anner đang t&igrave;m văn ph&ograve;ng của John. Một người phụ nữ đứng chờ xe bus. Anne hỏi c&ocirc; ấy" href="javascript:void(0)"><em>ANNE is looking for JOHN''s office. A WOMAN is waiting at a bus stop. ANNE approaches her.&nbsp;</em></a><br /><br /><a title="Xin lỗi" href="javascript:void(0)">ANNE:&nbsp;Excuse me.</a>&nbsp;<br /><br /><a title="V&acirc;ng" href="javascript:void(0)">WOMAN:&nbsp;Yes?&nbsp;</a><br /><br /><a title="C&ocirc; c&oacute; thể chỉ cho t&ocirc;i đến đường Michall được kh&ocirc;ng?" href="javascript:void(0)">ANNE:&nbsp;Could you tell me how to get to Mitchell Street?&nbsp;</a><br /><br /><a title=" V&acirc;ng. B&agrave; đang đi sai đường rồi đấy. Bạn cần phải đi thẳng dọc theo lối n&agrave;y, đi qua những quả cầu mầu bạc, rẽ tr&aacute;i, v&agrave; n&oacute; ở đường thứ hai b&ecirc;n phải, đối diện với t&ograve;a thị ch&iacute;nh" href="javascript:void(0)">WOMAN:&nbsp;Yes. You''re going the wrong way.&nbsp;You need to go straight along here, past the silver balls, turn left, and it''s the second on the right, opposite the Town Hall.&nbsp;</a><br /><br /><a title="C&aacute;m ơn b&agrave; rất nhiều" href="javascript:void(0)">ANNE:&nbsp;Thankyou very much.&nbsp;</a><br /><br />WOMAN:&nbsp;<a title="Ồ kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; g&igrave;" href="javascript:void(0)">You''re welcome.</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Anner đi theo sự chỉ dẫn. C&Ocirc; tiến đến gần 1 người b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng" href="javascript:void(0)"><em>ANNE follows the directions. She approaches a shopkeeper.&nbsp;</em></a><br /><br />ANNE:&nbsp;<a title="xin lỗi" href="javascript:void(0)">Excuse me.&nbsp;</a><br /><br />SHOPKEEPER:&nbsp;<a title="oh v&acirc;ng" href="javascript:void(0)"><span>Yes?&nbsp;</span></a><br /><br />ANNE:<a title="T&ocirc;i đang t&igrave;m số nh&agrave; 23. C&ocirc;ng ty th&aacute;m tử tư nh&acirc;n Barbour" href="javascript:void(0)">&nbsp;I''m looking for number 23. Barbour''s Private Investigator.&nbsp;</a><br /><br />SHOPKEEPER:<a title="ở dằng kia. gần nhựng c&aacute;i c&acirc;y" href="javascript:void(0)">&nbsp;Over there. Next to the trees.&nbsp;</a><br /><br />ANNE:&nbsp;<a title="Oh c&aacute;m ơn" href="javascript:void(0)">Oh. Thankyou</a>&nbsp;<br /><br />SHOPKEEPER:&nbsp;<a title="Ch&uacute;c may mắn. C&ocirc; sẽ cần đến n&oacute;" href="javascript:voi(0)">Good luck. You''ll need it.</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Anner đi v&agrave;o trong t&ograve;a nh&agrave; v&agrave; đi l&ecirc;n những bậc thang. C&ocirc; g&otilde; cửa" href="javascriot:void(0)"><em>ANNE enters the building and goes up the stairs. She knocks at the door.&nbsp;</em></a><br /><br />JOHN:&nbsp;<a title="Mời v&agrave;o" href="javascript:void(0)">Come in</a>!</p>\r\n<p><a title="Anner đi v&agrave;o v&agrave; nh&igrave;n xung quanh" href="javascript:void(0)"><em>ANNE enters and looks around.</em></a>&nbsp;<br /><br />JOHN:&nbsp;<a title="John(n&oacute;i trong điện thoại) V&acirc;ng, bất cứ khi n&agrave;o... v&acirc;ng gi&aacute; như thường lệ. Phải đi b&acirc;y giờ. Đ&uacute;ng. Tạm biệt Julia. Tạm biệt" href="javascript:void(0)"><span><em>(to ANNE)</em>&nbsp;Sorry.</span>&nbsp;<em>(to phone)</em>&nbsp;Yes, any time&acirc;&euro;&brvbar;yes usual rates. Must go now. Right. Goodbye. Julia. Bye.</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="John(n&oacute;i trong điện thoại) V&acirc;ng, bất cứ khi n&agrave;o... v&acirc;ng gi&aacute; như thường lệ. Phải đi b&acirc;y giờ. Đ&uacute;ng. Tạm biệt Julia. Tạm biệt" href="javascript:void(0)"><em>He hangs up and leaps to shake ANNE''s hand.</em>&nbsp;</a><br /><br /><a title="John(n&oacute;i trong điện thoại) V&acirc;ng, bất cứ khi n&agrave;o... v&acirc;ng gi&aacute; như thường lệ. Phải đi b&acirc;y giờ. Đ&uacute;ng. Tạm biệt Julia. Tạm biệt" href="javascript:void(0)">ANNE:&nbsp;Mr Barbour?&nbsp;</a><br /><br /><a title="T&Ocirc;i John, th&aacute;m tử tư. Chắc c&ocirc; l&agrave; Lee. XIn mời ngồi" href="javascript:void(0)">JOHN:&nbsp;John. Private investigator. You must be Ms Lee. Please sit down.</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="c&ocirc; l&agrave;m theo. Hơi lưỡng lự 1 ch&uacute;t" href="javascript:void(0)"><em>She does so, hesitantly.&nbsp;</em></a><br /><br /><a title="b&acirc;y giờ t&ocirc;i c&oacute; thể gi&uacute;p g&igrave; dc cho c&ocirc; Ms Lee" href="javascript:void(0)">JOHN:&nbsp;<span>Now - what can I do for you Ms Lee?</span></a></p>\r\n<p><a title="c&ocirc; ta đặt tấm ảnh của Davil l&ecirc;n b&agrave;n của &ocirc;ng ta" href="javascript:void(0)"><em>She puts the photo of DAVID on his desk.</em></a><br /><br />ANNE:&nbsp;<a title="anh c&oacute; thể gi&uacute;p t&ocirc;i t&igrave;m anh ấy được kh&ocirc;ng" href="javascript:void(0)">Could you find him for me?</a></p>', ''),
