(31, 'Ice Age 4: Continental Drift 2012 (2012)', 'ice-age-4-continental-drift-2012-2012', NULL, '<p><span class="style2"><img style="display: none;" src="http://www.tienganh123.com/file/video/trailer/bai148/bai148.jpg" alt="" width="214" height="317" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span class="style2">Grammar Note:</span></p>\r\n<p><span class="style2">1.No matter how long it takes, I will find you!&nbsp;</span><span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></p>\r\n<p><strong>No matter +&nbsp;</strong><em>who/what/which/where/when/how</em>&nbsp;+ Subject + verb in present: D&ugrave; c&oacute;... đi chăng nữa... th&igrave;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">No matter who</span>&nbsp;telephones, say I&rsquo;m out.&nbsp;(Cho d&ugrave; l&agrave; ai gọi đến th&igrave; h&atilde;y bảo l&agrave; t&ocirc;i đi vắng.)</p>\r\n<p>No matter who = whoever; No matter what = whatever.&nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline;">No matter what</span>&nbsp;(whatever) you say, I won&rsquo;t believe you.&nbsp;(Cho d&ugrave; anh c&oacute; n&oacute;i g&igrave; đi chăng nữa, t&ocirc;i cũng kh&ocirc;ng tin anh.)</p>\r\n<p><strong>It takes ...+ time:</strong>&nbsp;mất bao l&acirc;u (thời gian)</p>\r\n<p>=<em>&gt; D&ugrave; c&oacute; mất bao l&acirc;u đi chăng nữa, th&igrave; anh cũng sẽ t&igrave;m thấy em.</em></p>\r\n<p><span class="style2">2.Hey, little fellas. How about you and us against the pirates? You got no idea what I''m saying, do ya?</span>&nbsp;<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Fella:&nbsp;</strong>= fellow: Bạn, đồng ch&iacute;, g&atilde;, anh ch&agrave;ng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Against</strong>: Chống đối, phản đối.<strong>&nbsp;Pirate:&nbsp;</strong>Hải tặc</p>\r\n<p><strong>Have/ got no idea:&nbsp;</strong>Kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; &yacute; kiến g&igrave;, kh&ocirc;ng biết, kh&ocirc;ng hiểu</p>\r\n<p><strong>Ya</strong>: = You: (ng&ocirc;i thứ 2) bạn, cậu</p>\r\n<p