e can''t trust anyone.</p>\r\n<p><br /> (Franklin) Look at his face.&nbsp;<br /> (Evan) Look at my face.&nbsp;<br /> (Franklin) Look at his face and listen to me.&nbsp;<br /> Look at him and listen to me.&nbsp;<br /> --Look at me&nbsp;<br /> --Look at me&nbsp;<br /> (Franklin) Look at him and understand me. Look at both of us, but understand no one. Listen to my words, and hear his face.</p>\r\n<p><br /> (Franklin) I found something.&nbsp;<br /> (Evan) Nobody touches this ball until we figure out what it is.&nbsp;<br /> Whoa! Jeez! That''s terrible for the cow, but this thing''s awesome!&nbsp;<br /> Okay, first thing in war that''s lost is innocence.&nbsp;<br /> Yeah!</p>\r\n<p><br /> (Franklin) If you see anything from outer space, kill it.&nbsp;<br /> Die. Die.&nbsp;<br /> This things a goner for sure.&nbsp;<br /> Who wants to snap one with the Lizard man?&nbsp;<br /> Here we go.&nbsp;<br /> Oh, that looks good.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; line-height: 24.545454025268555px;" align="right">\r\n<table style="width: 501px;" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">\r\n<div align="right">\r\n<div id="download_1"><a style="font-size: 10pt; color: #336699; text-decoration: none;" href="http://download.tienganh123.com/trailer/bai153/bai153.zip" target="_blank"><strong>Download audio (MP3)</strong></a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="font-size: 10pt;">\r\n<div align="right">\r\n<div id="download_2"><a style="font-size: 10pt; color: #336699; text-decoration: none;" href="http://download.tienganh123.com/trailer/bai153/bai153.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>Download cả b&agrave;i v&agrave; phần dịch (PDF)</strong></a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', 0, NULL, '2012-10-26 0