(49, 'LISTENING', 'listening', NULL, '<h2 align="center">Listening</h2>\r\n<p align="center"><img src="http://tienganhphothong.tienganh123.com/file/phothong/lop6/bai1/listening/bai1_listening_ok_hello.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><em>You are going to listen to the chapter 1 "Hello-Introducing, Meeting People and Exchanging Greetings"&nbsp;</em>. Listen carefully and do the tasks that follows</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style="width: 670px;" border="0" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top" width="402">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="youtube" class="youtube"><object width="400" height="300" data="http://www.youtube.com/v/tU3lRm5W3oQ?fs=1&amp;hl=en_US&amp;rel=0" type="application/x-shockwave-flash"><param name="src" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/tU3lRm5W3oQ?fs=1&amp;hl=en_US&amp;rel=0" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /></object></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="258">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class="loibh">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Chapter 1 "Hello- Introducing, Meeting People and Exchanging Greetings".</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="translate"><input id="translate_button" type="button" value="Xem b&agrave;i dịch" /></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div id="show_mes">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>1</strong>.&nbsp;<strong>Word study</strong>: - Hello/Hi. - How are you? - I am fine, thanks. - How are you? - Very good!</p>\r\n<p><strong>2.Study the following sentences</strong>:</p>\r\n<p><strong>2.1. Formal</strong>: Good morning, my name is Natasha Rai. - Pleased to meet you Ms. Natasha. I am John Dsouza.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2.2. Informal</strong>: - Hi, I''m Natasha. - Pleased to meet you, I''m Sanjay.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2.1. Formal</strong>: - Good afternoon, Mother. - Good evening, Unchle Ramesh. - Good to see you again. - Good to see you too.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2.2. Informal</strong>: Hi Mom. - Hi, Ramesh Uncle. - How are you? - I''m fine, thank you.</p>\r\n<p><strong>3. Greeting according to the time:</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>3.1. Before 12:00 noon we say "Good morning"</strong>&nbsp;- Good morning, Mr Ramesh. - Good morning, Rashmi.</p>\r\n<p><strong>3.2. After 12:00 noon we say "Good afternoon"</strong>&nbsp;- Good afternoon, Ms. Sheela. - Good afternoon, Sir/Madam.</p>\r\n<p><strong>3.3. After 4:00pm we say "Good evening"</strong>&nbsp;- Good evening Madam. - Good evening, Amit.</p>\r\n<p><strong>3.4. Before we take a leave in the evening we say "Good night"</strong>&nbsp;- Good night Uncle. - Good night Sam.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<center>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div id="link_dl"><img src="http://data.tienganh123.com//file/dungchung/download.jpg" alt="" border="0" /></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div id="show_server"><img src="http://data.tienganh123.com/file/dungchung/server_vn.jpg" alt="" border="0" /></div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</center>\r\n<h3>Listening quiz</h3>\r\n<p><strong>B&agrave;i tập</strong></p>\r\n<center>Bạn h&atilde;y click v&agrave;o n&uacute;t "Start" để bắt đầu l&agrave;m b&agrave;i!<object id="sf2" width="600" height="500" data="http://tienganhphothong.tienganh123.com/file/phothong/lop6/bai1/listening/quiz1_nonVIP.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash"><param name="src" value="http://tienganhphothong.tienganh123.com/file/phothong/lop6/bai1/listening/quiz1_nonVIP.swf" /><param name="quality" value="high" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><param name="pluginspage" value="http://www.macromedia.com/go/getflashplayer" /></object></center>', '', 0, NULL, '2012-10-30 16:34:26', 2, 1, NULL, 55, '', '', '');
