e="font-family: Arial;">interj</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial;">xin lỗi</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">please</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode'';">/pliːz/</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">interj</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">xin, y&ecirc;u cầu</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">sit down&nbsp;</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode'';">/ˈsɪt.daʊn/</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">v</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">ngồi xuống</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">sugar</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode'';">/ˈʃʊg.əʳ/</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">n</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">đường</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">tea</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode'';">/tiː/</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">n</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">tr&agrave;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">tourist</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: ''Lucida Sans Unicode'';">/ˈtʊə.rɪ.z<sup>ə</sup>m</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">n</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">du kh&aacute;ch</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><br /><span style="font-family: Arial;">Expression - Th&agrave;nh ngữ</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><br />Excuse me:&nbsp;<em><span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span>&nbsp;xin lỗi anh/chị (d&ugrave;ng để g&acirc;y sự ch&uacute; &yacute; với ai trước khi giao tiếp với họ)<br /></em>Pardon<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span>:&nbsp;<em>xin lỗi, t&ocirc;i chưa nghe kịp, xin vui l&ograve;ng nhắc lại (l&ecirc;n giọng)<br /></em>(I beg your) Pardon&nbsp;<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span>&nbsp;= I''m sorry<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span>&nbsp;:&nbsp;<em>xin lỗi (xuống giọng, d&ugrave;ng tỏ &yacute; hối tiếc v&igrave; m&igrave;nh đ&atilde; phạm lỗi)<br /></em>Yes, please&nbsp;<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span>:&nbsp;<em>dạ v&acirc;ng/ No, thanks&nbsp;<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span>: th&ocirc;i, cảm ơn. (hai cụm từ n&agrave;y d&ugrave;ng trả lời khi được mời ăn hay uống c&aacute;i g&igrave;)<br /></em>to be from<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span>&nbsp;:&nbsp;<em>qu&ecirc; ở đ&acirc;u, từ đ&acirc;u đến<br /></em>to be on holiday&nbsp;<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span>:&nbsp;<em>đi nghỉ m&aacute;t</em></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span>Listening</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span><span style="font-size: medium;">Mời bạn nghe đoạn hội thoại sau:&nbsp;<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="translate"><input id="translate_button" type="button" value="Đ&oacute;ng b&agrave;i dịch" /></div>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n<div id="show_mes"><span style="color: #ff0000;">B&agrave;i học đ&atilde; được dịch, bạn h&atilde;y đưa chuột v&agrave;o c&aacute;c c&acirc;u tiếng Anh để xem.</span></div>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/file/baihoc/streamlineA/bai2/2.1.PNG" alt="" width="163" height="112" align="left" border="0" /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />I&nbsp;<span>Excuse me!</span><br />J&nbsp;<span>Yes?</span><br />I&nbsp;<span>Are you English?</span><br />J&nbsp;<span>Pardon?</span><br />I&nbsp;<span>Are you English?</span><br />J&nbsp;Oh, yes. Yes, we are.<br />I&nbsp;Oh, I''m English. Are you on holiday?<br />J&nbsp;No, we aren''t. We''re businessmen.<br /><br /><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/file/baihoc/streamlineA/bai2/2.2.PNG" alt="" width="162" height="114" align="left" border="0" /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="TitleColor"><span style="font-family: Arial;">J&nbsp;Please, sit down&hellip;<br />I&nbsp;Thank you.<br /><br /><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/file/baihoc/streamlineA/bai2/2.3.PNG" alt="" width="160" height="115" align="left" border="0" /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />J&nbsp;Tea?<br />I&nbsp;Yes, please.<br />J&nbsp;Sugar?<br />I&nbsp;No, thanks.</span></p>\r\n<p class="TitleColor"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><br /><br /><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/file/baihoc/streamlineA/bai2/2.4.PNG" alt="" width="165" height="142" border="0" /><br /><br />J.&nbsp;Where are you from?<br />I.&nbsp;I''m from London.<br />J.&nbsp;Are you a businessman?<br />I.&nbsp;No, I''m not. I''m a tourist.<br />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><strong><span style="font-family: Arial;">Grammar</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><strong>Ba đại từ c&ograve;n lại trong tiếng Anh</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table id="table22" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr id="tuvung">\r\n<td width="40%"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><strong>We</strong>&nbsp;(ng&ocirc;i thứ 1 số nhiều, chỉ những người n&oacute;i):&nbsp;<em>ch&uacute;ng ta, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i, bọn m&igrave;nh, bọn t&ocirc;i,...</em><br /><strong>You</strong>&nbsp;(ng&ocirc;i thứ 2 số nhiều, chỉ những người đang giao tiếp trực tiếp với người n&oacute;i):&nbsp;<em>c&aacute;c anh, c&aacute;c &ocirc;ng, c&aacute;c b&agrave;, c&aacute;c chị, bọn b&acirc;y, ch&uacute;ng m&agrave;y, ...</em><br /><strong>They</strong>&nbsp;(ng&ocirc;i thứ 3 số nhiều, chỉ những người hoặc vật được n&oacute;i tới - kh&ocirc;ng tham gia v&agrave;o c&acirc;u chuyện):&nbsp;<em>họ, c&aacute;c anh ấy, c&aacute;c chị ấy, c&aacute;c b&agrave; ấy, ch&uacute;ng n&oacute;, bọn họ, ...</em></span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table id="table23" style="width: 385px;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr id="tuvung">\r\n<td width="175"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><strong>Personal Pronouns</strong></span></td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top" width="175"><span style="font-family: Arial;">We<br />You<br />They<br /></span></td>\r\n<td valign="top"><span style="font-family: Arial;">''re<br />are<br />aren''t<br />are not</span></td>\r\n<td align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp; English.&nbsp;<br />&nbsp; American.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><strong>Nghe thử&nbsp;</strong><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<table id="table24" style="width: 384px;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top"><span style="font-family: Arial;">We are English.<br /></span></td>\r\n<td valign="top"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td align="left" valign="top" width="213"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><em>Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i l&agrave; người Anh.</em></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top"><span style="font-family: Arial;">We aren''t English.<br /></span></td>\r\n<td valign="top"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n<td align="left" valign="top" width="213"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><em>Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i kh&ocirc;ng l&agrave; người Anh.</em></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<table id="table25" style="width: 385px;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Are<br /></span></td>\r\n<td valign="top"><span style="font-family: Arial;">we<br />you<br />they</span></td>\r\n<td align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-family: Arial;">English?</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<table id="table26" style="width: 383px;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr id="tuvung">\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">Yes,</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">we<br />you<br />they</span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">are.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><br />No,<br /></span></td>\r\n<td valign="top"><span style="font-family: Arial;">we<br />you<br />they</span></td>\r\n<td align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-family: Arial;">aren''t.<br />are not.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<table id="table27" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr id="tuvung">\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;"><strong>Nghe thử</strong></span></td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Are they English?<br /></span></td>\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<p align="center"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><em>Họ c&oacute; phải l&agrave; người Anh kh&ocirc;ng?</em></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Yes, they are.<br /></span></td>\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<p align="center"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><em>V&acirc;ng, họ l&agrave; người Anh</em></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top"><span style="font-family: Arial;">No, they aren''t.<br /></span></td>\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<p align="center"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><em>Kh&ocirc;ng, họ kh&ocirc;ng phải l&agrave; người Anh</em></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><br />Trong tiếng Anh c&oacute; 3 ng&ocirc;i:</p