&nbsp;&nbsp; We với nghĩa "ch&uacute;ng ta&nbsp; sẽ bao gồm cả người n&oacute;i lẫn người nghe.<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<em>E.g.&nbsp; Can we go out now?<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yes, we can. Let''s go now.<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></em></p>\r\n<p><strong>Bảng chia động từ "To Be" thời hiện tại</strong></p>\r\n<table id="table29" style="width: 500px;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="119"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Dạng đầy đủ</span></td>\r\n<td width="111"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Dạng viết tắt</span></td>\r\n<td width="248"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Phủ định</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="119"><span style="font-family: Arial;">I am<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">I''m</span></td>\r\n<td width="248"><span style="font-family: Arial;">I am not&nbsp; (I''m not)<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="119"><span style="font-family: Arial;">You are<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">You''re</span></td>\r\n<td width="248"><span style="font-family: Arial;">You are not<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span>(You aren''t)</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="119"><span style="font-family: Arial;">We are<span><img src="http://www.tienganh123.com/icon/loa.gif" alt="" border="0" /></span></span></td>\r\n<td><span style="font-family: Arial;">